name: DAANA EDUCATIONAL WELFARE SOCIETY
briefDescription: Our society is a Non-Profitable Organization, established in 1999 at Ranga Reddy District, Hyderabad, Our motto is “Creation of Masters from Mass”.Continuing the Programmes • Education for Poor Peoples and their Children and also P.H. Students. • Conduct Health Camps, Eye Camps, Blood Donation Camps. • HIV & AIDS Control Awareness • Old age Welfare • Computer Training • Youth Welfare • Agriculture Development • Pure Drinking Water • Forestry & Greenery, Environment Awareness in Ranga Reddy, Medak, Nalgonda, Guntur, Prakasam Districts.
